        "accordion_jqMxxU": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "How long does dispatch and delivery take?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>YOUR ORDER WILL BE DISPATCHED WITHIN 24 HOURS OF YOUR ORDER BEING PROCESSED (ON BUSINESS DAYS).<br/><br/>FOR UK ORDERS ONCE DISPATCHED, ORDERS WILL ARRIVE:<br/><br/>UK: THE NEXT WORKING DAY</p><p>FOR INTERNATIONAL ORDERS ONCE DISPATCHED, ORDERS WILL ARRIVE:<br/><br/>PHORIA SHIPS WITH DHL EXPRESS AND FEDEX INTERNATIONAL. THE DELIVERY TIME WILL DEPEND ON YOUR LOCATION AND IS CALCULATED AT CHECKOUT. THIS RANGES FROM 1 - 5 DAYS DEPENDING ON YOUR CHOSEN METHOD.</p><p>PLEASE BE AWARE THAT UK PUBLIC HOLIDAYS WILL AFFECT YOUR EXPECTED DELIVERY DATE.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_wpmC4z": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Where does Phoria ship to and how much does it cost?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>PHORIA SHIPS WORLDWIDE. DELIVERY WITHIN THE UK IS FREE VIA ROYAL MAIL.</p><p>FOR EVERYWHERE ELSE YOU CAN CHOOSE BETWEEN:</p><p>FEDEX INTERNATIONAL - £20</p><p>DHL EXPRESS - £30</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_PPyQmH": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "When will my Pre-Order be dispatched?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>We will try to get your purchase sent out to you as soon as possible. Please check your confirmation email for all details including your estimated dispatch date. If you have any questions or want an update on your order please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> and we will get back to you within 24 hours.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_6HPKQd": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "How do I track my order?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>YOU CAN TRACK YOUR ORDER BY LOGGING INTO YOUR <a href=\"https://www.phoriajewellery.com/account/\" target=\"_blank\">ACCOUNT</a> OR REFERRING TO YOUR ORDER DISPATCH EMAIL. TRACKING DETAILS WILL BE EMAILED TO YOU AND ARE AVAILABLE FROM THE MOMENT YOUR ORDER IS DISPATCHED FROM US TO WHEN IT IS SIGNED FOR AT ITS FINAL DESTINATION.</p><p>REMEMBER TO CHECK YOUR JUNK/SPAM/PROMOTIONAL INBOX AS SOMETIMES TRACKING EMAILS MAY END UP IN THERE.</p><p>UK: ALL ORDERS ARE SHIPPED FULLY TRACKED VIA <a href=\"https://www.royalmail.com/sending/uk/special-delivery-guaranteed-1pm\" target=\"_blank\">ROYAL MAIL’S SPECIAL DELIVERY</a> SERVICE.</p><p>INTERNATIONAL: ALL ORDERS ARE SHIPPED FULLY TRACKED USING  FEDEX INTERNATIONAL AND EXPRESS SHIPPING VIA <strong>DHL EXPRESS WORLDWIDE.</strong></p><p>PLEASE NOTE THAT ALL PHORIA ORDERS REQUIRE A SIGNATURE ON DELIVERY WHETHER ORDERED FROM WITHIN THE UK OR INTERNATIONALLY.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_TDyU6j": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "What happens if I refuse my shipment?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>If you refuse your Phoria shipment, you are responsible for the shipping charges, any import fees and the cost of returning the parcel. In this instance, once the parcel has been received back, you will be refunded your total paid minus these costs.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_wjx7zt": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "What happens if my order hasn't arrived?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>The first thing is to check the tracking in the email sent to you when your order was dispatched to check the status of your parcel. If you are still worried about the whereabouts of your parcel after doing this, please get in touch at <a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> and we will be happy to help.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_BmELHi": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Duties + Taxes on orders outside of the UK?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>If you are ordering from outside of the UK your order will likely be subject to customs or import duties which will not be covered by Phoria. For more accurate information, we’d suggest getting in touch with your local customs office so you’re not surprised if there are any unexpected delivery charges at your end.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_wDbmiU": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "What happens if I refuse to pay customs?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>If you choose to refuse the customs fee and the parcel is returned back to Phoria, the shipping and handling fee will be deducted from your refund.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_MgVBF8": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Any other questions?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>If you have any other questions we are always happy to help, please email us at <a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> or for general enquiries <a href=\"mailto:studio@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>studio@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p>"
          }
        }
