        "accordion_G37ncM": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "DOES PHORIA OFFER RETURNS?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>WE REALLY HOPE YOU LOVE YOUR PHORIA PURCHASE! HOWEVER IF YOU DO WISH TO RETURN AN ITEM YOU CAN DO THIS BY GETTING IN TOUCH AT <a href=\"mailto:HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM </strong></a>WITHIN 14 DAYS OF RECEIVING YOUR GOODS. THEY THEN MUST BE RECEIVED BACK WITHIN 28 DAYS OF PURCHASE, UNUSED AND IN THEIR ORIGINAL CONDITION AND PACKAGING. PHORIA PROVIDES A RETURN SHIPPING LABEL FOR EASE BUT DOES NOT COVER THE COST OF RETURNS POSTAGE AND DOES NOT ACCEPT RETURNS ON EARRINGS (DUE TO HYGIENE REASONS). THANK YOU FOR YOUR UNDERSTANDING!<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_DwWwNc": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Does Phoria offer exchanges?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>IF YOU WISH TO EXCHANGE AN ITEM YOU CAN DO THIS BY GETTING IN TOUCH AT <a href=\"mailto:HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM </strong></a>WITHIN 14 DAYS OF RECEIVING YOUR GOODS. THEY THEN MUST BE RECEIVED BACK WITHIN 28 DAYS OF PURCHASE, UNUSED AND IN THEIR ORIGINAL CONDITION AND PACKAGING. PHORIA PROVIDES A RETURN SHIPPING LABEL FOR EASE BUT DOES NOT COVER THE COST OF EXCHANGE POSTAGE AND DOES NOT ACCEPT EXCHANGES ON EARRINGS (DUE TO HYGIENE REASONS). THANK YOU FOR YOUR UNDERSTANDING!</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_XNJUiB": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "How do I return or exchange my order?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>RETURNING OR EXCHANGING YOUR ORDER IS SUPER EASY. </p><ol><li>EMAIL US AT <a href=\"mailto:HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM </strong></a>AND TELL US WHY YOU WANT TO RETURN OR EXCHANGE YOUR ORDER. IF YOUR RETURN IS APPROVED WE WILL SEND YOU A PRE-PAID SHIPPING LABEL FOR YOU TO RETURN THE GOODS HOWEVER WE WILL DEDUCT THE SHIPPING FEE OFF OF YOUR REFUND OR WILL CHARGE FOR IT IF IT IS AN EXCHANGE.</li><li>RE-PACKAGE YOUR ITEM(S) CAREFULLY IN THEIR ORIGINAL PACKAGING ALONG WITH A NOTE STATING YOUR ORDER NUMBER, NAME AND REASON FOR RETURN.</li><li>STICK THE RETURN LABEL ONTO YOUR PACKAGE.</li><li>TAKE IT TO YOUR LOCAL FEDEX INTERNATIONAL OR DHL EXPRESS (IF INTERNATIONAL) OR ROYAL MAIL (IF UK) DROP OFF AND MAKE SURE YOU KEEP YOUR PROOF OF POSTAGE.</li><li>ONCE SHIPPED, RETURNS TAKE UP TO 3 DAYS TO BE RECEIVED BACK. ONCE RECEIVED WE WILL PROCESS THE RETURN OR EXCHANGE RIGHT AWAY.</li><li>IF IT IS AN EXCHANGE, WE WILL SEND THE EXCHANGE BACK TO YOU FREE OF CHARGE. YOU WILL RECEIVE UPDATED TRACKING ONCE SENT.</li></ol>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_9YMkiK": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Can I cancel or amend my order?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>Unfortunately, we are unable to cancel or amend orders once they have been placed. However, you can of course return your order once you have received it. Please get in touch at <a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> and we will be happy to help.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_TNhn7q": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Can I cancel or amend my pre-order?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>You can cancel at any time by emailing <a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> and we will get back to you within 24 hours. You will receive an email confirming the refund and should see the money back in the account you paid with within 5 working days depending on your bank.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_gdgbP7": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Can I change my email or shipping address on my Pre-order?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>Yes! Send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> with your updated details and we will get back to you within 24 hours to confirm it has been updated. You will then receive an updated pre-order confirmation email.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_YHHbXz": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "Faulty Items",
            "accordion__content": "<p>In the unlikely event that you receive a faulty item, or your item develops a fault, please do get in touch at<strong> </strong><a href=\"mailto:hello@phoriajewellery.com\"><strong>hello@phoriajewellery.com</strong></a> as we are always happy to resolve any issues.</p><p>Please also do so if your piece needs to be professionally re-plated, polished or repaired and we will share more info on our reconditioning service.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_dJKkzx": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "LIFETIME WARRANTY",
            "accordion__content": "<p>PHORIA OFFERS A LIFETIME WARRANTY ON ALL OUR PIECES. IN THE RARE CASE WHERE A PIECE MAY BE DEFECTIVE FROM PRODUCTION OUR WARRANTY COVERS ANY IMPERFECTIONS, BREAKAGES OR TARNISHING.</p><p>IF YOU ARE UNHAPPY WITH THE CONDITION OF YOUR PIECE, WE WILL EXCHANGE YOUR ITEM FOR A BRAND NEW PIECE AT NO ADDITIONAL COST. </p><p>CONTACT US AT <a href=\"mailto:HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM\" title=\"HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM\">HELLO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</a> FOR MORE INFORMATION OR ANY QUESTIONS YOU MAY HAVE ABOUT OUR LIFETIME WARRANTY.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_EtPGcW": {
          "type": "Accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion__title": "When will I receive my refund?",
            "accordion__content": "<p>Upon receipt of items, the credit or debit card originally used for the purchase will be credited with the cost of the goods, minus the delivery charges. We will process your refund within 5 working days of receipt. Your credit card company may take 4-7 working days to credit your account.</p>"
